[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":244},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002FSCSS\u002F20190416\u002F4026443340\u002F":3,"page:\u002FSCSS\u002F20190416\u002F4026443340\u002F":4,"alt:\u002FSCSS\u002F20190416\u002F4026443340\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002FSCSS\u002F20190416\u002F4026443340\u002F":221,"related:\u002FSCSS\u002F20190416\u002F4026443340\u002F":230},"\u002Fen\u002Fscss\u002F2019\u002F04\u002F16\u002Fscss-handbook-1-intro\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":204,"date":205,"description":206,"extension":207,"lang":208,"meta":209,"navigation":210,"path":211,"readingMinutes":212,"seo":213,"standalone":214,"stem":215,"tags":216,"tldr":218,"updated":218,"url":219,"__hash__":220},"content\u002FSCSS 學習手冊\u002FSCSS學習-前言(一).md","SCSS學習-前言(一)","4026443340",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":199},"minimark",[11,15,19,30,34,37,40,43,46,49,52,59,95,102,105,110,176,183,186,189,192,195],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"首先感謝六角學院- 廖洧杰校長所撰寫的 \"30天掌握 SASS 語法\" 這篇文章讓學習 SCSS 的我一直回頭學習，實在可以堪稱葵花寶典阿!!\n我在這邊基於校長這篇文章來嘗試撰寫一篇 SCSS 版學習 SCSS。",[16,20,21,22,29],{},"這邊也提供",[23,24,28],"a",{"href":25,"rel":26},"https:\u002F\u002Fithelp.ithome.com.tw\u002Farticles\u002F10126703",[27],"nofollow","30天掌握 SASS 語法","原文連結。",[12,31,33],{"id":32},"scsssass是什麼到底該學哪一個","SCSS\u002FSASS是什麼?到底該學哪一個",[16,35,36],{},"很多人都會念\"薩斯\"、\"沙士\"(唸起來根本一樣...)，然後都會覺得兩者名子不同應該是不同的東西，只是唸起來一樣而已。",[16,38,39],{},"依照我的解釋及觀念來講，SCSS 只是 SASS 新出的另一種 【CSS 預處理器】 寫法，相信聽到這 【CSS 預處理器】 有些人就會覺得好恐怖，其實不用擔心，SCSS\u002FSASS 東西只是對 CSS 擴充的語言而已。",[16,41,42],{},"也不用特別去思考到底學 SASS 還是 SCSS，因為當你學會寫 SCSS 的時候，其實 SASS 你已經無意間學會6~7成(部分寫法與SASS不同)。",[16,44,45],{},"這兩者差異在哪裡呢?\n直接來觀看比較快。",[16,47,48],{},"ps.這邊所使用的環境是 codepen 來做撰寫練習。",[16,50,51],{},"1.SASS 版本 (注意分號(:)後一定要空格，否則會出錯)",[16,53,54],{},[55,56],"img",{"alt":57,"src":58},"圖片","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F8kTJdPk.png",[60,61,66],"pre",{"className":62,"code":63,"language":64,"meta":65,"style":65},"language-sass shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast",".box\n   background-color: red\n   width: 50px\n   height: 50px\n","sass","",[67,68,69,77,83,89],"code",{"__ignoreMap":65},[70,71,74],"span",{"class":72,"line":73},"line",1,[70,75,76],{},".box\n",[70,78,80],{"class":72,"line":79},2,[70,81,82],{},"   background-color: red\n",[70,84,86],{"class":72,"line":85},3,[70,87,88],{},"   width: 50px\n",[70,90,92],{"class":72,"line":91},4,[70,93,94],{},"   height: 50px\n",[16,96,97],{},[23,98,101],{"href":99,"rel":100},"https:\u002F\u002Fcodepen.io\u002Fhsiangfeng\u002Fpen\u002FmvvBeX",[27],"SASS版本",[16,103,104],{},"2.SCSS 版本",[16,106,107],{},[55,108],{"alt":57,"src":109},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FjyZlNfe.png",[60,111,115],{"className":112,"code":113,"language":114,"meta":65,"style":65},"language-scss shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast",".box {\n   background-color: red;\n   width: 50px;\n   height: 50px;\n}\n","scss",[67,116,117,127,141,157,170],{"__ignoreMap":65},[70,118,119,123],{"class":72,"line":73},[70,120,122],{"class":121},"sCcAr",".box",[70,124,126],{"class":125},"sMAXC"," {\n",[70,128,129,132,135,138],{"class":72,"line":79},[70,130,131],{"class":121},"   background-color",[70,133,134],{"class":125},": ",[70,136,137],{"class":121},"red",[70,139,140],{"class":125},";\n",[70,142,143,146,148,151,155],{"class":72,"line":85},[70,144,145],{"class":121},"   width",[70,147,134],{"class":125},[70,149,150],{"class":121},"50",[70,152,154],{"class":153},"sWyjQ","px",[70,156,140],{"class":125},[70,158,159,162,164,166,168],{"class":72,"line":91},[70,160,161],{"class":121},"   height",[70,163,134],{"class":125},[70,165,150],{"class":121},[70,167,154],{"class":153},[70,169,140],{"class":125},[70,171,173],{"class":72,"line":172},5,[70,174,175],{"class":125},"}\n",[16,177,178],{},[23,179,182],{"href":180,"rel":181},"https:\u002F\u002Fcodepen.io\u002Fhsiangfeng\u002Fpen\u002FErrwKy",[27],"SCSS版本",[16,184,185],{},"SASS 少了括號、分號，主要用縮排，程式碼寫起來也比較乾淨，相較於 SCSS 學習曲線會比較高。\n如果對縮排定義不清楚的話，就很容易出現編譯錯誤，而導致學習上的困擾及撞牆。",[16,187,188],{},"相較之下 SCSS 與原本的 CSS 並無多大差異，對於新手來講是比較好上手，所以你問我初學想學 CSS 預處理器應該要挑一個，我想你看完前言就已經大概知道該怎麼選擇了。",[12,190,191],{"id":57},"![圖片]",[16,193,194],{},"對於寫 SCSS 到現在的心得來講，開發上效率先不談，但是對於想培養程式邏輯的人是一個很好入門的語言，因為 SCSS 中也是很像在寫程式語言，但是不會有太多的邏輯判斷。",[196,197,198],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sWyjQ, html code.shiki .sWyjQ{--shiki-default:#FF9492}",{"title":65,"searchDepth":79,"depth":79,"links":200},[201,202,203],{"id":14,"depth":79,"text":14},{"id":32,"depth":79,"text":33},{"id":57,"depth":79,"text":191},"SCSS","2019-04-16 20:03:12","首先感謝六角學院- 廖洧杰校長所撰寫的 \"30天掌握 SASS 語法\" 這篇文章讓學習 SCSS 的我一直回頭學習，實在可以堪稱葵花寶典阿!!","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fscss\u002Fscss-()","2",{"title":6,"description":206},false,"SCSS 學習手冊\u002FSCSS學習-前言(一)",[204,217],"SCSS 學習手冊",null,"\u002FSCSS\u002F20190416\u002F4026443340\u002F","EPniruaB62X-1oTgIabp4lozclIujocriZCqlQ11R1c",{"newer":222,"older":226},{"url":223,"title":224,"date":225},"\u002Flearnexp\u002F20190416\u002F3782185665\u002F","該如何正確的學習前端技術或程式語言","2019-04-16 22:36:38",{"url":227,"title":228,"date":229},"\u002Fnodejs\u002F20190415\u002F3558033712\u002F","Failed at the grpc@1.10.1 install script.","2019-04-15 20:34:42",[231,236,240],{"url":232,"title":233,"date":234,"readingMinutes":235},"\u002FSCSS\u002F20251123\u002F3919803484\u002F","SCSS 棄用 @import？！","2025-11-23 15:32:01","3",{"url":237,"title":238,"date":239,"readingMinutes":212},"\u002FSCSS\u002F20190421\u002F968240674\u002F","SCSS學習-mixin(五)","2019-04-21 07:24:30",{"url":241,"title":242,"date":243,"readingMinutes":212},"\u002FSCSS\u002F20190419\u002F947541843\u002F","SCSS學習-import(四)","2019-04-19 17:24:30",1784011683691]